Listing 7.3 Dockerfile
FROM golang:1.18 AS deps ❶
WORKDIR /hello-api ❷
ADD *.mod *.sum ./
RUN go mod download ❸
FROM deps as dev ❹
ADD . . ❺
EXPOSE 8080
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -ldflags "-w -X main.docker=true" \
 -o api cmd/main.go ❻
CMD ["/hello-api/api"]
FROM scratch as prod ❼
WORKDIR /
EXPOSE 8080
COPY --from=dev /hello-api/api / ❽
CMD ["/api"]
